sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant React as React Frontend
    participant Main as Main Server
    participant Cache as Main Cache
    participant DB as Main SQLite
    participant Worker as Worker Node

    React->>Main: POST /API/V1/Auth/Login<br/>X-Correlation-Id, X-Idempotency-Key, X-Auth-Action: Login<br/>{ Email, Password }
    Main->>DB: Verify hash, load User
    Main->>Main: Check Has2FAEnabled
    alt 2FA on
        Main-->>React: 200 JSON { Step: AwaitTotp, ChallengeId, PartialAuthJwt }
        React->>Main: POST /API/V1/Auth/TwoFactor/Verify<br/>X-Auth-Action: TwoFactorVerify<br/>{ Code, ChallengeId }
        Main->>Main: Validate TOTP
    end
    Main->>Cache: GET MainWorker:Company:{id}:WorkerNodeId
    alt cache hit
        Cache-->>Main: WorkerNodeId
    else cache miss
        Main->>DB: SELECT WorkerNodeId FROM Company
        DB-->>Main: WorkerNodeId
        Main->>Cache: SET (TTL 15m)
    end
    Main->>Main: Mint RS256 worker JWT (sub, cmp, wnk, aud, exp, roles, jti, kid)
    Main-->>React: 200 JSON { WorkerEndpoint, WorkerJwt, JwtExpiresAt }
    Note over React: JWT delivered in JSON body — never as cookie / localStorage / URL param.<br/>React stores it IN-MEMORY ONLY (useRef / Zustand non-persistent)<br/>per spec/19/12-jwt-delivery-contract.md §2. CSP per §5 mandatory.<br/>TTL <= 900s per spec/19/15-tunable-constants.md (WorkerJwtTtlSeconds).

    Note over React,Worker: All subsequent business calls bypass Main
    React->>Worker: GET /API/V1/Company/{slug}<br/>Authorization: Bearer <WorkerJwt><br/>X-Correlation-Id: <ULID>
    Worker->>Worker: Verify RS256 sig, kid, exp(skew=60s), aud=worker, wnk, iss<br/>per spec/19/12 §7
    Worker-->>React: 200 (data)

    Note over React,Main: Token refresh — single-use rotation (replay -> MAIN-400-09)
    React->>Main: POST /API/V1/Auth/Refresh (Main session cookie attached)
    Main-->>React: 200 JSON { WorkerJwt, JwtExpiresAt }
    Note over React: After page reload the in-memory JWT is gone;<br/>React must re-call /Company/{slug}/Resolve to obtain a fresh one.
